@HeathNaylor if you're still looking forward to work on that I'm happy to guide you through. I recommend to install [MonkeyType](https://github.com/Instagram/MonkeyType) and have it collect type information by running the tests.

MonkeyType doesn't generate perfectly annotated code but it's usually a good start from where some manual tweaks will get things in shape.

